@110 = ~Devastating Arrow~
@111 = ~These arrows were invented by a particularly devious mechanical genius. Underneath the tip is a small mechanism that allows it to split, each tip giving rise to three triangular projectiles on impact. Each triangle-shaped fragment then tears a different route through the target's body, wreaking havoc on his internal organs.

