Launcher: Bow

Weight: 0~
@112 = ~Arrow of Slaying~
@113 = ~This arrow is twisted and black, almost radiating evil as if possessed by something larger than itself. It was made specifically to kill one type of creature and one type only. In this case, the unlucky being is the umber hulk.

